    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "......好吧。我承认——我那天晚上去了鞋坊。但我只是去跟Frank谈生意的事。我没有碰他。是Vinnie——Vinnie说他到的时候看到Frank在床上睡觉......后来的事是Vinnie干的。",
    "enWords": "...Fine. I admit — I went to the shoe shop that night. But I only went to discuss business with Frank. I didn't touch him. It was Vinnie — Vinnie said when he arrived he saw Frank sleeping on the bed... what happened after was Vinnie's doing.",
