    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "Vinnie的详细供述里说得很清楚——他到鞋坊的时候，Frank已经'受伤倒在地上'。不是在床上睡觉。是倒在地板上，头部流血。",
    "enWords": "Vinnie's detailed statement is very clear — when he arrived at the shoe shop, Frank was 'lying injured on the ground.' Not sleeping on a bed. On the floor, bleeding from his head.",
