    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "如果你那晚只是去'谈生意'，你怎么会知道Vinnie到的时候Frank是什么状态？如果你没碰Frank，你怎么会编出'Frank在床上睡觉'这个说法？",
    "enWords": "If you only went there to 'discuss business,' how would you know what state Frank was in when Vinnie arrived? If you didn't touch Frank, why would you fabricate the claim that 'Frank was sleeping on the bed'?",
