    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "我那天晚上去找他，想最后谈一次。劝他别去。我告诉他如果举报，他自己也逃不掉——他也借了我的钱，他也签了那些文件。",
    "enWords": "I went to see him that night, wanted to talk one last time. To convince him not to go. I told him if he reports it, he won't escape either — he also borrowed from me, he also signed those papers.",
