    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "他......他当场就倒下去了。头上流了好多血......他不动了。我的眼镜也在撞击的时候摔碎了一片。我站在那里......我不知道自己站了多久。",
    "enWords": "He... he went down right there. So much blood from his head... he stopped moving. My glasses cracked from the impact too. I just stood there... I don't know how long I stood there.",
    "next": "260051",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
    "ParameterStr2": "",
