    "IdSpeaker": "NPC204",
    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "Margaret在隔壁房间......我不知道她有没有醒。我慌了。我打了电话给Vinnie——他是我唯一信得过的人。",
    "enWords": "Margaret was in the next room... I didn't know if she'd woken up. I panicked. I called Vinnie — he was the only person I could trust.",
    "next": "260052",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
