    "IdSpeaker": "NPC204",
    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "我告诉他出了事。他什么都没问......只是说'我来处理'。半小时后他就到了。他让我先走，剩下的他来。",
    "enWords": "I told him something happened. He didn't ask a single question... just said 'I'll handle it.' He was there in half an hour. He told me to leave, he'd take care of the rest.",
    "next": "260054",
    "script": "",
    "ParameterStr0": "",
    "ParameterStr1": "",
