    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "Vinnie纵了火。把一切都烧掉——包括Frank要去举报的那些文件。",
    "enWords": "Vinnie set the fire. Burned everything — including those documents Frank was going to use to report you.",
    "next": "260055",
