    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "然后你开始查了。Vinnie替我顶罪——他说是他干的一切。你知道为什么吗？",
    "enWords": "Then you started investigating. Vinnie took the fall for me — said he did everything. Do you know why?",
