    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "因为你用他母亲的安全做筹码。",
    "enWords": "Because you held his mother's safety as leverage.",
