    "IdSpeaker": "NPC204",
    "cnSpeaker": "莱昂纳德·罗斯",
    "enSpeaker": "Leonard Ross",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 2,
    "cnWords": "......不。不是威胁。我答应照顾他母亲——这是我们之间的约定。Vinnie自愿的。他说......他说他这辈子也还不清我对他的恩情。",
    "enWords": "...No. It wasn't a threat. I promised to take care of his mother — that was our arrangement. Vinnie volunteered. He said... he said he could never repay what I've done for him in this lifetime.",
