    "cnWords": "......（审讯室安静了很久。Leonard低着头，一只手捂住了脸。那副缺了一片镜片的眼镜摆在桌上。）",
    "enWords": "...(The interrogation room fell silent for a long time. Leonard hung his head, one hand covering his face. The glasses — one lens newer than the other — sat on the table.)",
