    "IdSpeaker": "NPC201",
    "cnSpeaker": "扎克·布伦南",
    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "Leonard Ross——真名Leonardo Russo。你因谋杀Frank Kowalski被正式逮捕。你有权保持沉默，你所说的一切将作为呈堂证供。",
    "enWords": "Leonard Ross — real name Leonardo Russo. You are under arrest for the murder of Frank Kowalski. You have the right to remain silent. Anything you say can and will be used against you in a court of law.",
