    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "（Leonard站了起来，双手自觉地伸到身前。他没有反抗。那个在South Side呼风唤雨的银行家，此刻看起来只是一个疲惫的老人。）",
    "enWords": "(Leonard stood up, holding his hands out in front of him. He didn't resist. The banker who once ruled the South Side now looked like nothing more than a weary old man.)",
