    "enSpeaker": "Zack Brennan",
    "talkDisplayIndex": 1,
    "cnWords": "（鞋坊纵火案，结案。凶手：Leonard Ross。纵火犯：Vinnie Moretti。动机：Frank Kowalski发现Leonard的掠夺性贷款计划并试图举报。Leonard先杀人灭口，Vinnie后纵火毁证。一个波兰鞋匠的正义，最终还是没能被烟灰掩埋。）",
    "enWords": "(The shoe shop arson case, closed. Killer: Leonard Ross. Arsonist: Vinnie Moretti. Motive: Frank Kowalski discovered Leonard's predatory lending scheme and tried to report it. Leonard silenced him first, Vinnie burned the evidence after. A Polish cobbler's pursuit of justice — in the end, it couldn't be buried under the ashes.)",
